<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>A blur effect blurs the source. This effect is useful for reducing details, such as when the source loses focus and you want to draw attention to other elements. The level of detail can be modified using the setBlurRadius() function. Use setBlurHints() to choose the blur hints.</db:para>
<db:para>By default, the blur radius is 5 pixels. The blur radius is specified in device coordinates.</db:para>
